> **📚 Complete Documentation**: See [README.md](README.md)

## ✨ Features

- 🏗️ **Clean Architecture** - Well-structured layers (Infrastructure, Domain, Host)
- 🔄 **SignalR** - Real-time communication with auto-mapped hubs
- 📨 **RabbitMQ** - Event-driven messaging system
- 💾 **Redis** - Distributed caching
- 🗄️ **EF Core** - Multi-database support (PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQL Server)
- 📊 **Swagger/OpenAPI** - Automatic API documentation
- 📝 **Serilog** - Structured logging
- ⏰ **Background Jobs** - Cron-based task scheduling
- 🐳 **Docker Ready** - Complete containerization support

## 🚀 Quick Start

```powershell
# 1. Install template
.\Install-Template.ps1

# 2. Create your project
dotnet new nexusstack -n MyAwesomeProject

# 3. Advanced configuration
dotnet new nexusstack -n MyAwesomeProject \
  --DatabaseProvider MySQL \
  --EnableSignalR true \
  --IncludeMQService false \
  --TargetFramework net10.0

# 4. Run your project
cd MyAwesomeProject
dotnet run --project Host\MyAwesomeProject.WebAPI
```

## 📖 Documentation

- [Template Usage Guide](TEMPLATE_USAGE.md) - Installation, configuration, development

## 🔧 Quick Commands

- **Install**: `dotnet new install .`
- **Create**: `dotnet new nexusstack -n <ProjectName>`
- **Help**: `dotnet new nexusstack --help`
- **Uninstall**: `dotnet new uninstall NexusStack.Template`

## 📦 What's Included

```
YourProject/
├── Infrastructure/           # Core utilities and models
├── Domain/                   # Business logic
│   ├── YourProject.Core/
│   ├── YourProject.EFCore/
│   ├── YourProject.Redis/
│   ├── YourProject.RabbitMQ/
│   └── ...
├── Host/                     # Application entry
│   └── YourProject.WebAPI/
└── BackgroundServices/       # Background workers
```

